So my name is Ray Paik.

00:34.000 --> 00:37.000
Currently, we have a community at CUBE.

00:37.000 --> 00:41.000
If you're not familiar with CUBE, we're in the semantic layer space of data analytics.

00:41.000 --> 00:45.000
So if you want to find out more, check out our website at cube.dev.

